			<div class="dablink">This article is about Thomas Gold, an Austrian astrophysicist.  For Thomas Ruggles Gold, a United States Representative from New York, see <a href="/wiki/Thomas_R._Gold" title="Thomas R. Gold">Thomas R. Gold</a>.</div>
