<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Thomas_Gold&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> Gold is buried in the rear section of the cemetery.</li>
